    <section id="id8746812">
      <title>SAFETY AND FIRST AID IN THE KITCHEN</title>
      <para id="id8789158">ACTIVITY 1: </para>
      <para id="id7176746">To be able to name and apply the rules regarding safety in the kitchen.</para>
      <list id="id1169006602404" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>There are a number of dangers in the kitchen. There are various places and utensils that can cause injuries if not used with the necessary care. It is extremely important that rules regarding safety in the kitchen be followed. These include, for example, that stoves should be used correctly and that safety rules regarding electricity be applied.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1169006599335">4.1 Give ten general rules for safety in the kitchen.</para>
      <para id="id1169006582200">4.2 Give three safety measures for when you use a stove.</para>
      <para id="id8791561">4.3 Give three safety aspects regarding electricity in the kitchen.</para>
